=== MIRROR_WRITING ===
# id: 63
# title: The Mirror Writing Puzzle
# chinese_title: 反字谜
# category: Puzzle
# mode: dungeon

A terminal displays Chinese characters, but they're mirrored — written backward. You need to mentally flip each character to read the access code. The challenge tests spatial reasoning and character recognition simultaneously.

* [Mentally reverse the characters and enter the code]
  ~ gain_radical("白")
  "反" (fǎn) — reverse, opposite, anti-
* [Use a reflective surface to read them]
  ~ gain_xp(20)
  "镜" (jìng) — mirror
* [Write them out on your datapad to decode]
  ~ gain_xp(15)
  "写" (xiě) — to write
